#

Tacos al Pastor

45 min
$12
300 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main CourseStreet Food

Tags:

QuickEasyMexicanDinner

Description

Delicious marinated pork served in soft tortillas with fresh toppings, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal!

Ingredients

  • pork shoulder: 1 pound
  • pineapple: 1 cup, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • cilantro: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • lime: 2, juiced
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • chili powder: 2 tablespoons
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • oregano: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • salsa: for serving
